## Session 7: Error Handling & Debugging

Effective error handling is a mark of production-quality code. JavaScript has several built-in error types and patterns for creating informative, catchable errors.

### Built-in Error Types

| Type | When thrown |
|------|-------------|
| Error | Base type; thrown manually |
