## Session 8: Modules & Bundling

JavaScript's module system evolved from ad-hoc globals through CommonJS to the native ES Module standard. Understanding both is critical in a Node.js ecosystem that bridges both worlds.

### CommonJS (Node.js default pre-ESM)

```javascript
